  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bb0\u0bc8\u00a0 \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf, \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The anti-government struggle will intensify again if the central bank governor is removed - a letter from a ruling party member to the president and prime minister",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The people's struggle against the government will intensify if Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe, the governor of the Central Bank, who is recognized and trusted by the people, is sacked as public opposition to the government has eroded more than the political structure of politicians.",
        "PA MP Jagath Kumara has sent a letter to the President and the Prime Minister urging them to drop any resolutions to remove the Governor.",
        "Following reports on social media that the government is trying to remove Central Bank Governor Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe from the post of Governor. Whether this news is true or just a rumor will be examined secondary.",
        "The decision taken by the people of the country in view of this news will further aggravate the current crisis situation.",
        "The decisions of the former Governor of the Central Bank and top officials of the Central Bank are being criticized by the people of the country as the main reason for the current worst economic crisis and the short-sighted actions of the politicians are another reason for the economic crisis.",
        "Public confidence in politicians and government officials has waned. In such a context, when it was mentioned that a Governor of the Central Bank should be appointed to gain the trust and recognition of the people, Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe was summoned to the country in a crisis situation and appointed as the Governor of the Central Bank.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Governor of the Central Bank, Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe, has implemented progressive resolutions in a short period of time. Advancing resolutions in the state structure that would undermine the duties of the public officer to accept responsibility in a crisis situation will further strengthen the current crisis situation.",
        "The people's struggle against the government will intensify again if Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe, the governor of the Central Bank, who is recognized and trusted by the people, is sacked as public confidence in the political structure is now eroded among the people more than politicians and various protests against the government have intensified.",
        "The Governor of the Central Bank should be given the opportunity to continue serving the country."
      ],
